{"TopicId":122162,"ForumId":34,"TopicTitle":"[Min KSP: 1.12.2] Deep Space Exploration Vessels - Build NASA Inspired Ships In KSP","CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-10-02T15:56:13Z","PageNum":16,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"ISE","CreatedById":161984,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-21T11:14:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222926727\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221484790717\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn January 18, 2017 at 6:51 PM, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith the Clydesdale now complete, I looked at my roadmap for the next release of DSEV. The next tough project will be the centrifuge, but I already have ideas on how to spin the IVA along with the external model. The tough part will be seeing if I can have the IVA follow the external model as its folds up. If not, that\u0027s ok. Anyway, last month \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022111501\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kuzzter\u003C/a\u003E suggested an inline variant of the Clydesdale, and I\u0027m pleased to say that the exterior model came together rapidly. I need to flip the front name tag around, but it\u0027s otherwise good to go.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/gYAhI1D.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022gYAhI1D.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/gYAhI1D.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just need to make a variant of the Clyde\u0027s IVA to account for the new form factor, but it will otherwise work fine for the Danube Delta. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy god that is so gorgeous! And some people and I have been testing the ASET props, the only thing that he is trying to get around to is the release. So using the beta from github as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/60950-moardv/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002260950\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/60950-moardv/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MOARdV\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0said, is a good idea for head start! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-21T16:37:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222929375\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221484997249\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161984\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ISE\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, ISE said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMy god that is so gorgeous! And some people and I have been testing the ASET props, the only thing that he is trying to get around to is the release. So using the beta from github as \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/60950-moardv/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002260950\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/60950-moardv/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MOARdV\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0said, is a good idea for head start! \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ll look into it. Maybe I can cut my dev time down by reusing what I did for the Buffalo as a basis. It will have to wait until next week though, I have personal stuff going on this weekend. Might be able to finish the stock IVA though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T01:42:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGetting close to done:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/ETrC46h.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022ETrC46h.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/N6bC04z.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022N6bC04z.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bwVvgx5.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022bwVvgx5.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/OKHtajg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022OKHtajg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/N6ragaf.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022N6ragaf.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nStock IVA is pretty much good to go. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNow I\u0027ll see if I can adapt the Buffalo ASET IVA to the Clyde and save some time that way. If that works then I can apply it to the Danube, and those monitors up front will be able to use the ASET MFD screens. I wish I could get the \u0022pong\u0022 monitors to show external views like RPM can..\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Montieth","CreatedById":57608,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T05:46:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstead of the pong screens, how about the usual RPM MFDs\u0027output\u00A0with the controls for the large forward wall mounted screens in the panel in front of the kerbal?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat way you can throw a forward camera image up as well as orbital data.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-22T15:51:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222930244\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485064006\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257608\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Montieth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, Montieth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nInstead of the pong screens, how about the usual RPM MFDs\u0027output\u00A0with the controls for the large forward wall mounted screens in the panel in front of the kerbal?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat way you can throw a forward camera image up as well as orbital data.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s actually the plan. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E What you see is the stock IVA, so that there\u0027s something available if you don\u0027t have RPM \u0026amp; ASET installed. Ideally, those pong screens will let you see camera views in addition to images from your Screenshots folder, but I\u0027ve yet to figure that out. I\u0027m also looking at an ASET version; seeing \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111360-justjim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022111360\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111360-justjim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@JustJim\u003C/a\u003E and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E use the Buffalo with ASET got me thinking about modifying the Buffalo\u0027s ASET IVA despite my earlier concerns- basically, they reminded me of just how cool ASET props look. And when \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/60950-moardv/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002260950\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/60950-moardv/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@MOARdV\u003C/a\u003E releases Avionics Systems, I\u0027ll support that as well. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T22:12:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57608-montieth/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002257608\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57608-montieth/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Montieth\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Just Jim\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022111501\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kuzzter\u003C/a\u003E Here is the Danube Delta\u0027s ASET IVA:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPilot\u0027s Station:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/lezh2Yg.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022lezh2Yg.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(NOTE: There is no digital altimiter that I could find)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCopilot\u0027s Station:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/StIlvUb.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022StIlvUb.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCaptain\u0027s Chair:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/vJ1uyZH.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022vJ1uyZH.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFlight Engineer\u0027s Station:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/Q8alxfQ.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022Q8alxfQ.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSystems Engineer\u0027s Station:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/VdpNkCW.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022VdpNkCW.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n10 Forward:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/hM1STB6.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022hM1STB6.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have some reworking to do for the Clydesdale before its IVA is done.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T22:13:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933265\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485295931\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57608-montieth/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002257608\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/57608-montieth/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Montieth\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Just Jim\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289014\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89014-adsii1970/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@adsii1970\u003C/a\u003E\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022111501\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kuzzter\u003C/a\u003E Here is the Danube Delta\u0027s ASET IVA:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow.... I need a drool bucket... \u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-24T22:45:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222933269\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485296030\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022148725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Just Jim\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n30 minutes ago, Just Jim said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWow.... I need a drool bucket... \u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks! I have a couple more, these are from the Clydesdale:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/oNjUw2y.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022oNjUw2y.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/sRFEQn9.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022sRFEQn9.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T01:38:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith the Clyde and Danube Delta finally done, I\u0027m starting in on the D2 centrifuge. First, here is a reference image, NASA\u0027s Discovery II:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022The_Discovery_II_(front_view).jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022595\u0022 src=\u0022https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a4/The_Discovery_II_(front_view).jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd here is what I\u0027ve got thus far:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/2qc19vugrxs?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"smotheredrun","CreatedById":165894,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-25T02:07:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106975\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106975-angel-125/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Angel-125\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0wow!!! \u00A0Those consoles are cool!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T03:39:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMore progress tonight:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/9vQc7yMCsFY?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe GUI is still being worked on, but the basic centrifuge rotation code is working just fine. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E I know \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/142617-thereadpanda/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022142617\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/142617-thereadpanda/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@TheReadPanda\u003C/a\u003E was among the people asking about a centrifuge in one of my mods, it\u0027s definitely on the way!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-26T03:40:40Z\u0022 title=\u002201/26/2017 03:40  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 26, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Angel-125\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DStaal","CreatedById":155685,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T03:44:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the cross-section of that joint?\u00A0 (It doesn\u0027t look like a Kerbal should be able to go through it to me.\u00A0 The round part\u0027s fine, but the half-rounds to the sides look a bit small.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T03:46:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222934722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485402266\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022155685\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DStaal\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, DStaal said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat\u0027s the cross-section of that joint?\u00A0 (It doesn\u0027t look like a Kerbal should be able to go through it to me.\u00A0 The round part\u0027s fine, but the half-rounds to the sides look a bit small.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0.625m by 1.25m, plenty of room for a kerbal to fit through. I\u0027ve checked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-26T03:46:25Z\u0022 title=\u002201/26/2017 03:46  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 26, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Angel-125\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"smotheredrun","CreatedById":165894,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T04:06:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222934723\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485402366\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n20 minutes ago, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n0.625m by 1.25m, plenty of room for a kerbal to fit through. I\u0027ve checked.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003E* Wernher checked by grabbing Bob and stuffing him through progressively smaller tubes with a plunger until Bob got stuck (@ 0.3m). \u00A0Wernher then used a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Inventory System (mod)\u0022\u003EKIS\u003C/abbr\u003E/\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E grapple to pull him back out. \u00A0The medical staff say that Bob\u0027s head will loose its new traffic cone shape within the next few weeks - Kerbal medical researchers are still trying to determine if Kerbalnaut skulls are made of bone or sponge based upon the numerous crazy contraptions that various \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E administrators employ to get said Kerbalnauts into space (or into the ground).\u003C/em\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSomeone should animate this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-26T04:06:59Z\u0022 title=\u002201/26/2017 04:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 26, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by smotheredrun\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-26T04:14:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne more for the night:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00221Tbvk0i.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/1Tbvk0i.png\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Montieth","CreatedById":57608,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-27T07:56:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat look nice. I like how you\u0027ve incorporated one of the methods of stacking the ship in such a way that things work for the crew\u0027s apparent downward gravity\u00A0while they\u0027re under thrust.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-30T01:08:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been slogging through the centrifuge this weekend, unwrapping and texturing and making it all look right is taking some time, but I\u0027ve made progress:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022CjsPmer.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CjsPmer.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"smotheredrun","CreatedById":165894,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-30T05:41:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooking good! \u00A0I may even be able to use this in my current career save! (Just started)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"smotheredrun","CreatedById":165894,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-31T01:53:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a quick question:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose \u0022crew cans\u0022 on the ends of the folding crew tubes, will they be hard mounted or will the user be able to attach other \u0022cans\u0022? I.e. other labs/modules, etc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-31T02:02:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222939722\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485827631\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022165894\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022smotheredrun\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 minutes ago, smotheredrun said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a quick question:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose \u0022crew cans\u0022 on the ends of the folding crew tubes, will they be hard mounted or will the user be able to attach other \u0022cans\u0022? I.e. other labs/modules, etc\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey are hard mounted, but you\u0027ll have multiple templates to choose from to configure the centrifuge. Plus, the crew can mesh will serve as the basis for a separate part; you\u0027ll have a hab, lab, and greenhouse crew can in addition to the D2 Centrifuge. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want the ability to mount your own parts, use the existing Spindle, Hub, and Counter Torque Ring along with Infernal Robotics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-01-31T02:04:23Z\u0022 title=\u002201/31/2017 02:04  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 31, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Angel-125\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"smotheredrun","CreatedById":165894,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-01-31T04:01:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222939729\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485828179\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you want the ability to mount your own parts, use the existing Spindle, Hub, and Counter Torque Ring along with Infernal Robotics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLol Which I broke, stranding Jeb, Bob, Munsen, and a few \u0022Red Shirts\u0022 on what is now a Kerbol escape trajectory\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-01T05:42:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGetting there...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022HYFXAZT.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HYFXAZT.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwaster","CreatedById":71262,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-01T11:43:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222938665\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485738487\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106975\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Angel-125\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 1/29/2017 at 8:08 PM, Angel-125 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been slogging through the centrifuge this weekend, unwrapping and texturing and making it all look right is taking some time, but I\u0027ve made progress:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CjsPmer.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022CjsPmer.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022562\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/CjsPmer.jpg\u0022 width=\u00221000\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a suggestion... ignore it or implement it as you will.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut instead of those joints, how about flexible / inflatable tubes encased in a folding framework (kind of like the folding framework that connected Skylab and the Apollo telescope mount)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Angelo Kerman","CreatedById":106975,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-01T18:43:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222941038\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022122162\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221485949388\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002271262\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starwaster\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Starwaster said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust a suggestion... ignore it or implement it as you will.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut instead of those joints, how about flexible / inflatable tubes encased in a folding framework (kind of like the folding framework that connected Skylab and the Apollo telescope mount)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf you can show me how to rig and animate such a configuration, then I can consider it. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Montieth","CreatedById":57608,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-02-01T18:56:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think from a mechanical perspective, a sliding elbow might be more workable.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThe joints rotate against each other which, when the two wedges are slipped in opposite directions makes the tube straight instead of an elbow.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022galvanized_elbow.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.spsmsys.com/shared/dbi/product/image/clifco/galvanized_elbow.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}